        Professor

        Description: Constructs a new Professor object with the provided information. This constructor initializes a new Professor object with the specified first name, last name, ID, and base salary.

        Preconditions:

        • firstName must be a String.
        • lastName must be a String.
        • id must be a String.
        • baseSalary must be a String.
        • totalSalary must be a double.

        Postconditions:

        • A new Professor object is created with the specified first name, last name, ID, base salary and total Salary.
        Parameters:
        firstName - The first name of the professor.
        lastName - The last name of the professor.
        id - The ID of the professor.
        baseSalary - The base salary of the professor.
        totalSalary - The total salary of a professor.
